Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是真正的海龙神社
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人就在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  钥匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)\fn方正粗活意简体\an5\fs45}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N飞出  蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积满了苔藓很滑  要小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:00:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:04.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人是怎样的神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为到现在为止谁都没有见过他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.83,0:01:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上的主人们所保护的神究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  和行人在一起就没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海龙大人的叫声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好滑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫声停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的愿望是传达不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因就是…海龙大人会先听取我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是海龙大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人  请务必实现我的愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  还带了供奉用的红豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好这里有根绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡子…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人  请保佑行人能离开这岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地震吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口被…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是胡子  大概是海龙大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我不知情的情况下好像不小心拉断了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像拉断了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  居然把海龙大人的胡子给拽下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.92,0:04:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太让人吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会受到天罚的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是因为你们太没用了我才去阻碍他们祈愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是失败了偶然中拽下来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这样一来  海龙大人也不会保佑行人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子  也只能放弃离开岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看吧  这样一来行人就属于我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何会变成绫音的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个和那个是两回事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会承认的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终女婿大人会选择你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的喜欢他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是应该考虑究竟如何做才为女婿大人好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么对行人来说是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人正准备出海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人能观察到远处的式神所看到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是送你到中途吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有海龙大人的保佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么能带小铃去那么危险的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸猪排也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一起去的话才会担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人就该保护女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚来这岛上的时候确实什么都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在已经变得很可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:06:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不得不去救美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样  也不能让小铃深处险境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人也没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  女婿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让行人走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你真的觉得这样做可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有…这样做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是女婿大人所盼望的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算失去生命也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:55.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鱼片…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鱼片
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  快去追行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到漩涡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能越过那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真笨  明明不可能有这种事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道不该这样做…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:08:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我不要与行人永别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  快回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鱼片  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么说都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不过没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差点就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生鱼片  去海龙大人所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算从海面上过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.32,0:10:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:20.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  生鱼片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始我一人去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必保佑行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.47,0:11:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人  请息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人  请保佑行人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃姐  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  为什么会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从上面入口进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个炸开了一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想救行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让你一人把风头全抢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真罗嗦  我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不率直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不是故意的  我真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人  真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人  请保佑公子平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保护行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请救救行人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人  请实现小铃和行人的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海龙大人  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必保护行人  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:14:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒是…那就是海龙大人的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人现在已经在漩涡外面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你所期望的吗  西部的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎才是  不是故意让他通过的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的想法都是一致的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女婿大人  如果能离开岛的话  那并不是他一人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是因为行人拥有能让大家能为之如此付出的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这微妙的刺法有点难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还…还以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说这里是岛外了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是来接我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安无事啊  收到信我很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这样一来好像变成是哥哥遇难了我赶来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是好笑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  有精神就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  没事真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始就很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实呢  在哥哥离家出走后我就马上出海来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后所乘的船遇到暴风雨  沉入海底了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  醒来的时候已经被漂流到一个不知名的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那岛很有趣既没有电视也没有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做饭要用柴烧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼也要自己钓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔬菜有那么大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  对了  那岛叫蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是只有男人的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这些就是岛民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好人是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的担心是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别喊我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我们没有因不纯的动机对美咲有过任何侵犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有谁让美咲悲伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很笨拙  但一直被大家所帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在非常的高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以还想再在蓝兰岛生活一会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听些奇闻也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  哥哥也一起过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很欢迎哥哥您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这暴风雨来之前不穿越漩涡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去是…要回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回我的 蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的…蓝兰岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有人在等着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲  就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  也请小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速出发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.77,0:18:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  明明看得到岛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无论几次都被推回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然从外面进去是绝对不可能的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要跟行人永别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着吧  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不可能的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对…没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴风雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心女婿大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人绝对没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在一定见到妹妹美咲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记行人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许还会有新的女婿大人会漂流进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老婆婆  在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说曹操曹操就到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.47,0:20:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.18,0:21:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  又相见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞蛾扑火自取灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然自愿回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二回  争夺女婿大人捉迷藏大会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  女婿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.86,0:21:38.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争夺女婿大人捉迷藏大会要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则就不用我介绍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何  我没听过这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女婿大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道他一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.54,0:22:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是不应该勉强回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野先生  吃早饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  那家伙为什么还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢  还没分出胜负呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅  偷袭太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你逃的
